Glenn Ford, 65, was diagnosed with stage four lung cancer shortly after being released from prison in Angola last year .
Ford was too weak to stand when he was released last year and was too frail to stand at the scene of the shooting of a jeweler .
Marty Stroud, 63, was found dead in his Louisiana home after the fatal shooting .
Stroud wrote a letter to Ford telling him that he could not forgive him for what he had done as a young lawyer .
'It's a stain on me that will be with me until I go to my grave,' he wrote .